description.html:
We're back for 2021 and kicking off with a slightly different format for January.

Joining us is the marvellous Tom Geraghty from Red Hat Open Innovation Labs to talk about resilience engineering, psychological safety and socio-technical systems.

After his talk, he'll be running an interactive discussion session with Q&A for all our attendees!
